  Location, CalendarItem.calendar_id → Calendar → Store, CalendarItem.organizer_id
  → Participant → Identity, invitees = Participant.owner_id with entity_type = 7,
  Attachment.owner_id / file_id → AttachmentFile), the Participant.status mapping
  (0/7 no response, 1 accepted, 2 declined, 3 maybe), Calendar.sharing_status
  (0/1/2), the "_float" floating-timezone sentinel, and the Cocoa-seconds
  timestamp conversion — attributed inline in calendar/schema.go,
  calendar/types.go and deploy/diff_calendar.py. iLEAPP is also the differential
